						               													<description>Expansion for Bamboleo.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game components:&amp;#10;long wooden &amp;quot;balance&amp;quot;spaced shelf&amp;#10;wooden round stick to balance the shelf&amp;#10;instructions&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game comes in a tube.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This expansion adds another layer to Bamboleo. Players now play in pairs. Each pair has to put their lifted blocks on one of the 8 spaces on &amp;quot;their&amp;quot; side of the balance.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The object of the game for the teams is to win the balance. It's smart to place the heaviest pieces on the outside of the balance.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Additional rules&amp;#10;If a player breaks of his attempt of taking a block form the Bamboleo board, the other party is allowed to take a block from the balance.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If a player passes to take a block from the Bamboleo board, and the other teams manages to still pull a block from the Bamboleo board, the other team may also take a block from the balance.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
